  "A neutral, unbiased question": "",
  "The first question on the survey": "",
  "A question worded to push respondents toward a particular answer": "",
  "A question about leadership qualities": "",
  "A leading question uses loaded or suggestive wording that steers the respondent toward a specific response.": "",
